platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We wouldnt be surprised if Subway Surfers kept its spot near the top of the charts for decades to come. Its heart is the key to its stamina, revealed in loving details lavished on cities from Chicago to Shenzhen in its World Tours or in the lovable ruffians awarded in its frequent events. Its a cinch to pick up, but were still finding new ways to master it years and miles later.
This blockbuster runnerkeeps charging ahead with loads of rewards to chase and special events set in cities across the world.
